                            Award-winning food fanatic. Prone to fits of apathy. Pop culture fan. Typical creator.
                            Twitter aficionado. Social media guru. Unable to type with boxing gloves on. Amateur tv fanatic.
                            Total coffee ninja. Analyst. Explorer. Travel practitioner. Creator. Freelance food fanatic. Twitter specialist.
                            Thinker. Beer trailblazer. Web scholar. Alcohol guru. Bacon fanatic. Organizer. Problem solver.
                            Typical social media geek. Web buff. Bacon aficionado. Thinker. Professional alcohol fanatic.
                        </h4>
                        <hr>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="row gutters-sm">
                    <div class="col-sm-6 mb-3">
